    </div>
    <div class="parallax"><img src="/images/rouletteBackground1.jpg" alt="Unsplashed background img 1"></div>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="section">

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col s12 center">
                <h4>Ingresa tu saldo</h4>

                <p class="left-align light">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam scelerisque id nunc nec volutpat. Etiam pellentesque tristique arcu,
                    non consequat magna fermentum ac. Cras ut ultricies eros. Maecenas eros justo, ullamcorper a sapien id,
